819.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-12589\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-23.35.00-1024x819.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-23.35.00-300x240.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-23.35.00-768x614.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-23.35.00-563x450.jpeg 563w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-05-at-23.35.00.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2fd9c8b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2fd9c8b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-25eadc9 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"25eadc9\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-56d843a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"56d843a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>Itinerary Overview<\/h3>\n<p><b>Day 1: Marrakech to Zagora Desert<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Drive to Zagora: Start your journey with a scenic drive from Marrakech through the Atlas Mountains and Draa Valley, passing traditional Berber villages along the way (approx. 6 hours).<\/p>\n<p>Arrival in Zagora: Upon arrival, enjoy a local lunch before continuing to your desert camp.<\/p>\n<p>Camel Trek into the Desert: Ride camels into the heart of the Zagora Desert, where you\u2019ll experience the tranquility of the dunes.<\/p>\n<p>Overnight at Desert Camp: Enjoy a traditional Berber dinner and spend the night in a luxury desert camp under the stars.<\/p>\n<p><b>Day 2: Zagora to Marrakech<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Sunrise in the Desert: Wake up early to watch the beautiful sunrise over the desert dunes, a truly magical experience.<\/p>\n<p>Return Camel Ride: After breakfast, ride back to the starting point.<\/p>\n<p>Drive Back to Marrakech: Depart from Zagora and return to Marrakech, arriving in the late afternoon or evening.<\/p>\n<p><\/p>\n<p>&#8212;<\/p>\n<p><b>What&#8217;s Included<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Transportation by air-conditioned vehicle<\/p>\n<p>Camel trek into the Zagora Desert<\/p>\n<p>Overnight stay in a desert camp<\/p>\n<p>All meals as per the itinerary<\/p>\n<p>Professional guide\/driver<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>2 Day Zagora Desert Adventure Experience the beauty of Morocco&#8217;s Sahara desert with a short but unforgettable trip to Zagora. This 2-day journey will immerse you in the desert&#8217;s serene landscapes, Berber culture, and stunning sunsets. Itinerary Overview Day 1: Marrakech to Zagora Desert Drive to Zagora: Start your journey with a scenic drive from [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":11314,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-11650","page"